comment2.text=\r\n\ Called\ automatically\ by\ Swing\ to\ paint\ the\ component.\r\n\ Iterates\ through\ all\ active\ game\ objects\ and\ calls\ their\ draw()\ method.\r\n\ @param\ g\ The\ Graphics\ object\ used\ for\ drawing.\r\n
