comment3.text=\r\n\ This\ method\ is\ called\ repeatedly\ by\ the\ gameLoopTimer.\r\n\ It\ contains\ the\ core\ game\ logic\ for\ updating\ object\ states,\ spawning,\ and\ collisions.\r\n\ @param\ e\ The\ ActionEvent\ generated\ by\ the\ Timer.\r\n
